{"lastModified":1776260992858,"uri":"c::7819217464::vessel::d5cccd28-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Turkey\n\nRefitted in 2025, CANEREN offers an abundance of both interior and exterior space for guests thanks to her large motor yacht style saloon and extended flybridge. There is capacity to accommodate up to 8 passengers in 4 guest cabins which include 3 very comfortable double cabins and a pullman triple cabin. She is an ideal choice for 3 couples looking for a yacht with equal size accommodation for each couple. There is flexibility to offer fine dining on the aft deck as well as the flybridge. Lazy days on the Med are what is awaiting guests on board CANEREN but plenty of water toys on board and a crew of 4 to make sure everything is catered for means you can always have action whenever you want.","blueprint":{"name":"CANEREN","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cccd28-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::8f8b6490-bd82-11ef-b585-a71fd936cda4/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cccd28-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::8f798a40-bd82-11ef-b585-a71fd936cda4/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cccd28-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::8f5623c0-bd82-11ef-9f70-b52b29717ceb/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cccd28-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::8f96d640-bd82-11ef-b585-a71fd936cda4/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cccd28-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::8f67fe10-bd82-11ef-9f70-b52b29717ceb/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cccd28-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::8f796330-bd82-11ef-a3ef-49aa0d29d3e3/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cccd28-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::8f8b6490-bd82-11ef-a3ef-49aa0d29d3e3/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cccd28-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::8f7ac2c0-bd82-11ef-9f70-b52b29717ceb/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cccd2